import React from 'react'
import {} from 'semantic-ui-react'

class NewsFeeds extends React.Component{

    render(){

        return(
            <Segment>
      
                <Comment.Group> 
                  <Comment>
                    <Comment.Avatar as='a' src='https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/b4339e6c847f4f25822532330320548e?d=identicon' />
                    <Comment.Content>
                      <Comment.Author>LamSonhai</Comment.Author>
                      <Comment.Metadata>
                        1:00pm
                      </Comment.Metadata>
                      <Comment.Text>
                        sssdass
                      </Comment.Text>
                     <Label attached  as='a'>
                      <Icon name='thumbs up outline' />
                     </Label>
                    </Comment.Content>
                   
                  </Comment>
                </Comment.Group>
          
            </Segment>
        )
    }

}

export default NewsFeeds
